Class Folder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.telenav.kivakit.core.filesystem.Folder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FileSystemObject, ModificationTimestamped, java.lang.Comparable<Folder>
    public class Folder
extends java.lang.Object
implements FileSystemObject, java.lang.Comparable<Folder>
    Folder abstraction that adds type safety and various helpful methods. Support for various file systems is implemented in kivakit-filesystems.
    Author:
    jonathanl (shibo)
